<br />But they don't, so I have to debug them.
<br />I'm thinking on developing a graphical debugger pretty much like the one in FCEUXD SP.
<br />Those who made emulators, how did you do this? did you make a debugger? did you use an IDE's debug? did you use any other solution?</div>

