				<table width="100%" cellspacing="5">
				<tr>
					<td>
					

						<div class="postbody">I'd recommend getting <a href="http://nickmass.com/images/nestest.nes" class="postlink">nestest.nes</a> to pass first.
<br />
<br />It will make sure your CPU is correct.  Start with getting the PC/registers to match perfectly, and then get your cycle timings correct.
<br />
<br />Load the ROM into your emulator's memory and set the 6502 PC to C000.  Turn off interrupts.
<br />
<br />Build a tracelogger to match this format (note those are PPU cycles, not CPU cycles).  Run and then compare your log against this golden log:  <a href="http://nickmass.com/images/nestest.log" class="postlink">http://nickmass.com/images/nestest.log</a></div>

					<br clear="all" /><br />

